So he was messing with everybody's medication.

37:38.620 --> 37:40.529
Making us all sicker.

37:40.530 --> 37:43.019
And then he sent us to that fountain.

37:43.020 --> 37:44.279
That's it.

37:44.280 --> 37:46.459
So after we drank,

37:46.460 --> 37:49.110
He'd give us some real medication.

37:50.940 --> 37:53.059
Making us all feel better.

37:53.060 --> 37:54.350
And it worked.

