38:04.170 --> 38:06.760
Well, so much for miracles.

38:19.350 --> 38:20.939
Thank you, mr. Monk.

38:20.940 --> 38:23.640
This is the best christmas I can remember.

38:23.640 --> 38:24.959
Yeah. I was just doing my job.

38:24.960 --> 38:26.249
No, it wasn't just that.

38:26.250 --> 38:27.449
Thanks for the caring.

38:27.450 --> 38:29.279
