38:37.630 --> 38:38.589
No, we insist.

38:38.590 --> 38:39.809
After all you've done for us.

38:39.810 --> 38:41.349
No, no, no, he means he literally can't take it.

38:41.350 --> 38:43.279
I got it, though. Thank you so much.

38:43.280 --> 38:44.169
Merry christmas.

38:44.170 --> 38:45.539
