39:21.410 --> 39:22.399
That's all I can say.

39:22.400 --> 39:23.609
Randy, when I drank that water,

39:23.610 --> 39:24.469
Something happened.

39:24.470 --> 39:26.759
It was like a slate inside me was wiped clean

39:26.760 --> 39:28.700
And I started over.

39:30.810 --> 39:32.580
