39:39.580 --> 39:41.610
Um, I almost forgot.

39:42.180 --> 39:43.970
This is for you.

39:45.920 --> 39:47.560
Merry christmas.

39:52.150 --> 39:53.469
Jared, hey!

39:53.470 --> 39:55.440
